nodes.text: The Mission to Uukaablis was a New Republic mission to the planet Uukaablis in the Kathol sector of the Outer Rim Territories in 8 ABY. The CR90 corvette FarStar traveled to the planet in an attempt to find a cure for a bioweapon deployed by the Qektoth Confederation.
